---
/** Vision section: against / instead / who for. Design-system cards + icons. */
---

<section id="vision" class="section home-vision" aria-labelledby="vision-heading">
  <div class="app-container">
    <header class="home-vision__header">
      <p class="section-eyebrow">Vision</p>
      <h2 id="vision-heading" class="home-vision__title">
        A calm, co-owned space in a captured internet
      </h2>
      <p class="body-text home-vision__lead">
        Most platforms are optimized to harvest attention and data. Palchat is built for something else: people who want to own their digital life, think clearly, and build tools that answer to them — not to an ad exchange.
      </p>
    </header>

    <div class="home-vision__grid">
      <article class="card home-vision__card">
        <div class="home-vision__icon home-vision__icon--against" aria-hidden="true">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
            <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10" />
            <path d="m4.9 4.9 14.2 14.2" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="section-title home-vision__card-title">
          What we stand against
        </h3>
        <ul class="body-text-small home-vision__list">
          <li>Infinite feeds and engagement loops that treat people as metrics.</li>
          <li>Surveillance advertising and &quot;personalization&quot; that quietly profiles you.</li>
          <li>Black-box platforms where you can&apos;t see or change how things work.</li>
        </ul>
      </article>

      <article class="card home-vision__card">
        <div class="home-vision__icon home-vision__icon--for" aria-hidden="true">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
            <path d="M12 3a6 6 0 0 0 9 9 9 9 0 1 1-9-9Z" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="section-title home-vision__card-title">
          What we build instead
        </h3>
        <ul class="body-text-small home-vision__list">
          <li>Simple, legible tools you can understand and explain end to end.</li>
          <li>Spaces for writing and conversation without feeds, likes, or ads.</li>
          <li>Features that prioritize custody of your ideas over growth hacks.</li>
        </ul>
      </article>

      <article class="card home-vision__card">
        <div class="home-vision__icon home-vision__icon--who" aria-hidden="true">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
            <path d="M16 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-4-4H6a4 4 0 0 0-4 4v2" />
            <circle cx="9" cy="7" r="4" />
            <path d="M22 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-3-3.87M16 3.13a4 4 0 0 1 0 7.75" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="section-title home-vision__card-title">
          Who Palchat is for
        </h3>
        <ul class="body-text-small home-vision__list">
          <li>People who refuse to be reduced to data points.</li>
          <li>Builders who want to co-own their stack and community.</li>
          <li>Teams who care more about autonomy than &quot;time on site&quot; charts.</li>
        </ul>
      </article>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .home-vision {
    padding-top: var(--sp-7);
    padding-bottom: var(--sp-8);
  }

  .home-vision__header {
    max-width: 720px;
    margin-bottom: var(--sp-6);
  }

  .home-vision__title {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    line-height: 1.3;
    color: var(--color-text-primary);
    margin-top: var(--sp-2);
    margin-bottom: var(--sp-3);
  }

  .home-vision__lead {
    margin: 0;
  }

  .home-vision__grid {
    display: grid;
    gap: var(--sp-5);
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
  }

  @media (min-width: 768px) {
    .home-vision__grid {
      grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
      gap: var(--sp-5);
    }
  }

  .home-vision__card {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
  }

  .home-vision__icon {
    width: 44px;
    height: 44px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    border-radius: 12px;
    margin-bottom: var(--sp-4);
  }

  .home-vision__icon svg {
    width: 24px;
    height: 24px;
  }

  .home-vision__icon--against {
    background: var(--color-error-bg);
    color: var(--color-error);
  }

  .home-vision__icon--for {
    background: var(--color-primary-light);
    color: var(--color-primary);
  }

  .home-vision__icon--who {
    background: var(--color-success-bg);
    color: var(--color-success);
  }

  .home-vision__card-title {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    margin-bottom: var(--sp-3);
  }

  .home-vision__list {
    margin: 0;
    padding-left: 1.1rem;
    list-style: disc;
  }

  .home-vision__list li {
    margin-bottom: var(--sp-2);
  }

  .home-vision__list li:last-child {
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }
</style>
